a^2+b^2 = c^2
a,b
c
a^3+b^3 = c^3
(3,4,5), (4,4,5)
a=0,b^2=c^2\implies b=\pm c
b^3=c^3\implies b=c
\implies b=c
(0,b,b)
(b,0,b)
c\ne0, \left(\frac ac\right)^2+\left(\frac bc\right)^2=1
\implies \frac ac<1\implies \left(\frac ac\right)^2>\left(\frac ac\right)^3
\left(\frac bc\right)^2>\left(\frac bc\right)^3
\implies \left(\frac ac\right)^3+\left(\frac bc\right)^3<1
